{"tid":301576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】iPhone十年改變生活習慣　打工仔最怕WhatsApp","createTime":"2017-06-28T17:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T08:01:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bde0ca0d241d8068cc3f2cf0d46c90ce1447ec07","tid":301576,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017年6月28日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXmZBRAwQ3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlXmZBRAwQ3k&d=jzoBtcDn5a4I92ZefLOOqVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=83146f28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXmZBRAwQ3k</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170628/large/vsub63401.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170628%2Flarge%2Fvsub63401.jpg&h=c1fdcf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人說科技越進步，人與人之間越變得冷漠，十年前在2007年6月29日第一部iPhone正式面世，世界從此變得不一樣，大家也不自覺變了低頭族。<br />\n<br />\n以前想煲外國劇或動畫卡通，都用電腦下載某某程式，對比當時其他手機實體鍵盤，iPhone革命性玩3.5吋大螢幕，配合YouTube開創手機看片先河，令大家漸漸地變成了低頭族，機不離手，上下班都可以拿手機看劇。<br />\nApple自2008年推出App store，也將手機變成遊戲天堂，不同廠商也紛紛開發遊戲程式，《Angry Bird》、《Candy Crush》等遊戲曾經風靡一時，發展到今天推出了不同卡通精品，《Candy Crush》更加有大電影。不過眾多App當中，打工仔對WhatsApp一定又愛又恨，以前放工奉旨不收電郵，現在基本上24小時候命，放工放假都要覆訊息，已讀不回更加是死罪。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170628/large/vsub63403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170628%2Flarge%2Fvsub63403.jpg&h=83d8c877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對比iPhone7的1,200萬像素鏡頭，當年第一部iPhone只有200萬像素鏡頭，規格不算最強，但卻帶動了手機上網新潮流，加上社交媒體興起，2010年及2011年Instagram及Snapchat相繼面世，隨之手機拍攝功能亦越來越強勁，十年間由200萬像素提升到1200萬像素鏡頭，加上後製效果，人人也可以當攝影師。不過上網打卡也要付出代價，以前大家仍用2G計劃，電話費數十元就可以了，iPhone觸控操作才真正令流動上網更方便，網絡用量需求大增，3G也不夠快，要4G！每月6G數據用量也經常爆Data。無可否認iPhone重新定義手機用途，打機、上網、睇片，不知十年後大家會否仍在用iPhone18？"},{"pid":"ef274baf691c59277fdb8c5b6a297b009fad3b3f","tid":301576,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a024c056add76c420525038a64c2db5233c747","tid":301576,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:28:42.000Z","msg":"閃靈二人組幾好睇"},{"pid":"325d867abd96da3cb6987ef2b92bb71373830d9e","tid":301576,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:12:58.000Z","msg":"仲有令生果公司，向其他聲稱「仿製iPhone 類似外型、介面」嘅科技公司，<br />\n發動專利訴訟戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最經典嘅莫過於生果 vs *** 嘅專利戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277c1fdbcbc7a24dcbfa3f7c6468c344e3e50071","tid":301576,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"越同社交有關既科技真係越戇鳩"},{"pid":"52bf9d56ea79b082367b64f50af5620411990a3b","tid":301576,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚唔鍾意 whatsapp 可以洗左佢"},{"pid":"83a7cfb1f3624a2cf74febf9326c14c796f322b6","tid":301576,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"事實真係iphone 帶起"},{"pid":"2989655eda744469d30d5e1c92a5ea800bd12281","tid":301576,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}